{"tid":1849620,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大S捐一萬口罩給武漢，汪小菲實力護妻，回應質疑：出於人道主義","createTime":"2020-01-29T06:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T05:14:38.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a961e3f3650405080bb5ebfc6158c22e628bf8f9","tid":1849620,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:58:38.000Z","msg":"大S捐一萬口罩給武漢，汪小菲實力護妻，回應質疑：出於人道主義<br />\n<br />\n武漢疫情逐漸發展，全世界各地均出現確證案例。不止大陸，台灣、香港、日本的口罩都被代購們搶購一空。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics5.baidu.com/feed/42a98226cffc1e17b8d4eacf1677d605718de9d6.jpeg?token=85e0533657f72fe39fe1e13a53efd03c&amp;s=D700E1A146A789EB5220341B03008000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics5.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2F42a98226cffc1e17b8d4eacf1677d605718de9d6.jpeg%3Ftoken%3D85e0533657f72fe39fe1e13a53efd03c%26s%3DD700E1A146A789EB5220341B03008000&h=5ca3d526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但在抗擊新型冠狀病毒的前線，許多醫務工作者卻仍缺少口罩、護目鏡、防護服。他們甚至自發在社交平台發出征集社會物資捐助的文章。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics0.baidu.com/feed/d000baa1cd11728ba8c1e043961be3c8c1fd2cd4.jpeg?token=19ff435df105a4edc1f49fab6abd7f15&amp;s=8950EC121D9FD0C85ACDD1CF0100C0B2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics0.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2Fd000baa1cd11728ba8c1e043961be3c8c1fd2cd4.jpeg%3Ftoken%3D19ff435df105a4edc1f49fab6abd7f15%26s%3D8950EC121D9FD0C85ACDD1CF0100C0B2&h=1654e559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1月27日，大S丈夫汪小菲在社交平台發文表示，妻子大S是台灣人，她在日本採購了一萬個口罩，將要寄往武漢，幫助疫區解決物資短缺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics2.baidu.com/feed/d1160924ab18972b174d9434ba2a5b8f9c510ac2.jpeg?token=6bc1d5b5063166cc69ad326fb6599fbc&amp;s=5092EC3B9DD86DCA5A6984D20000C0B3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics2.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2Fd1160924ab18972b174d9434ba2a5b8f9c510ac2.jpeg%3Ftoken%3D6bc1d5b5063166cc69ad326fb6599fbc%26s%3D5092EC3B9DD86DCA5A6984D20000C0B3&h=9465a089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此前1月24日，台灣當局表示N95、外科口罩開始管制一個月，禁止出口，確保台灣供應，與其他地區伸出援手形成鮮明對比。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics7.baidu.com/feed/0824ab18972bd40781f1574f276ebe570eb309bf.jpeg?token=f48d182eeda872118e7fea44ad68ca8d&amp;s=46301FC586431D55214C39A003007000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics7.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2F0824ab18972bd40781f1574f276ebe570eb309bf.jpeg%3Ftoken%3Df48d182eeda872118e7fea44ad68ca8d%26s%3D46301FC586431D55214C39A003007000&h=a26507d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在1月28日早，大S轉發了丈夫的動態，並表示蒐集口罩、捐贈口罩只是每個人都應有的做人態度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics5.baidu.com/feed/962bd40735fae6cd3502890351542f2243a70f0e.jpeg?token=be0399fb8817728bb19f5d02ab0ec6f0&amp;s=4098CC3B01EECCE94C5524DE010080B3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics5.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2F962bd40735fae6cd3502890351542f2243a70f0e.jpeg%3Ftoken%3Dbe0399fb8817728bb19f5d02ab0ec6f0%26s%3D4098CC3B01EECCE94C5524DE010080B3&h=8ef95b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大S夫婦此舉充滿了人道主義精神。大陸網友紛紛表示感謝，並稱讚大S人美心善。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/622762d0f703918f2acc2ea50fda069158eec4a9.jpeg?token=258522b603f450e6662c698df6c85ea4&amp;s=18267D33014E754D125DA5DA0000C0B3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics4.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2F622762d0f703918f2acc2ea50fda069158eec4a9.jpeg%3Ftoken%3D258522b603f450e6662c698df6c85ea4%26s%3D18267D33014E754D125DA5DA0000C0B3&h=e68482c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小S也轉發表示支持姐姐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics1.baidu.com/feed/6c224f4a20a44623da5e7a13c6c552080df3d71d.jpeg?token=3788515e29a8508f8b69dcf2962455ae&amp;s=4892EC1397A07D031A5884C70000C0B3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics1.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2F6c224f4a20a44623da5e7a13c6c552080df3d71d.jpeg%3Ftoken%3D3788515e29a8508f8b69dcf2962455ae%26s%3D4892EC1397A07D031A5884C70000C0B3&h=80e3493e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相對於錢款，武漢前線對口罩的需求更大，大S夫婦的行為對疫區非常有意義。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics1.baidu.com/feed/a6efce1b9d16fdfaed162271e868ac5295ee7b20.jpeg?token=0ff362dcec1399a1817a115a78a71c29&amp;s=3E786484461337D25538E52503000083\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics1.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2Fa6efce1b9d16fdfaed162271e868ac5295ee7b20.jpeg%3Ftoken%3D0ff362dcec1399a1817a115a78a71c29%26s%3D3E786484461337D25538E52503000083&h=58a8bd41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣藝人范瑋琪更是在社交媒體上對台灣當局義憤填膺，呼籲人們關注災情。台灣藝人界對災情的關注讓人感慨同胞的關懷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/c2cec3fdfc0392456dd84070d97384c47c1e2549.jpeg?token=1291d761a742ffd65d4db17f90b1093d&amp;s=5B8B9B474F1153D49A98D4FE03008031\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics3.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2Fc2cec3fdfc0392456dd84070d97384c47c1e2549.jpeg%3Ftoken%3D1291d761a742ffd65d4db17f90b1093d%26s%3D5B8B9B474F1153D49A98D4FE03008031&h=7ec1ec98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一方有難，八方支援。除了汪小菲大S夫婦，娛樂圈的明星藝人們紛紛開始伸出援手。1月2日，朱一龍鼓勵即將上前線的醫護人員，還捐款100萬。"},{"pid":"b22a3d79a850a917fcd910f3663d9a62ad66e228","tid":1849620,"uid":44171,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"台灣入唔到WHO佢老婆有冇屌過支那唔人道?"},{"pid":"68a23e4ae0f613c5d3139969faf02e73bac3ec45","tid":1849620,"uid":225130,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:00:59.000Z","msg":"人你老母<br />\n台灣人唔係人?<br />\n<br />\n自己國家有難自己工廠整飽佢啦屌"},{"pid":"d094b60322303d229c181edf62642ea79e35bda5","tid":1849620,"uid":272652,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"台灣冇事咩而家？全世界都冇口罩你地就出賣真正自己人"},{"pid":"880d78262f5f5c06c9dd0da1c3d14b1536b74769","tid":1849620,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"台灣比共產黨打壓既時候<br />\n唔知呢班飲台灣人奶水大既偽人講過d咩?"},{"pid":"3b30943d9132093c1b3d8cad9c3b82988093e708","tid":1849620,"uid":2772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:05:23.000Z","msg":"人民幣主義咋掛<br />\n台灣人唔係人咩?"},{"pid":"48db9ba28c7d700013fd5178eaa7891bd48b1914","tid":1849620,"uid":168564,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"人道主義X<br />\n人民幣主義O"},{"pid":"b32f39d5eb8d8816115d079dc4b7edf66f98c5f1","tid":1849620,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"他們都是支那狗，完。"},{"pid":"e3157b4ae18aa2392fe3f371a808f4980a0452e9","tid":1849620,"uid":49336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"達哥都叫香港人戴口罩<br />\n大s小s竟然叫台灣人送口罩去大陸..."},{"pid":"0e481eeb8f2ee3b4f720d298709355a1684eafed","tid":1849620,"uid":149877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"台灣人屌撚硬佢"},{"pid":"a2022e87be3735894b8f84b07b28c28f805b4120","tid":1849620,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"搵人傳去日本叫佢地截住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fe3165d1bc040dc76f32f71820c47a80d7f296","tid":1849620,"uid":112241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"以佢地身家，拿三四萬蚊做場公關show....抵撚到爛。之後大陸市場又大賺返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醒目"},{"pid":"b81e2234dba00d8724787fe892d453e5600ae53e","tid":1849620,"uid":144024,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"呢幾隻真係臭雞黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武漢瞞報爆到大大獲，佢唔屌<br />\n大陸延遲式封關搞到疫情四散至全球，佢唔屌<br />\n台灣保護自己國民，限買口罩，佢拍撚晒片屌<br />\n<br />\n自己喺日本高調做蝗虫掃口罩去「幫手」，喊撚晒口拎光環，屌佢老母。<br />\n人地日本人又唔撚洗口罩？<br />\n始作俑者又唔出文拍片喊住屌？<br />\n<br />\n奶共奶撚到食屎狗咁"},{"pid":"f7384345ca3d91bc5a779b0cf051d8b800339233","tid":1849620,"uid":236165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48db9ba28c7d700013fd5178eaa7891bd48b1914","tid":1849620,"uid":168564,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"人道主義X<br />\n人民幣主義O"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:11:47.000Z","msg":"終於有人心水夠清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4593cee41139ef92dd2b483bed46f8ddec9d33c3","tid":1849620,"uid":87852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB